						               													<description>Welcome to DKR Rally Raid, considered one of the toughest and most famous rallies in the world. Try to finish each stage in the shortest time possible, carefully following the roadbook. Overcome the inconveniences that arise, taking care of the car from the difficulties of the terrain and enduring the unfavorable weather to win this difficult competition. Let's race!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The objective is to finish 6 stages obtaining the lowest overall time. Each stage consists of going with your car from point A: start; to point B: finish line. In each game turn you must roll 2 dice, assign one for your direction and one for your speed, and find out their meaning in the roadbook to move the car according to your choice. In each stage, the terrain and the weather will make your life difficult. At the end of some stages you can repair damage to the vehicle, but sometimes you will have to repair damage in the middle of the race. At the end of the sixth and last stage, the winner will be the one who gets the lowest overall time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
